@import '../common/css/variable'

.el-container 
  min-width 715px
  height 100%
  .el-header 
    box-shadow 0 4px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08)
    margin-bottom 10px
    .header-menu-warp 
      position relative
      float right
      height 60px
      line-height 60px
      width 120px
      padding 0
      display flex
      .avatar
        width 50%
        height 100%
        margin 8px
        img
          width 44px
          height 44px
          border-radius 50%
      .loginOut
        width 50%
        text-align center
        cursor pointer
    .header-logo 
      display inline-block
      width 250px
      height 100%
      background url('../common/images/logo.png') no-repeat 16px center;
  .m-body 
    .aside 
      height 100%;
      width 140px;
      background none repeat scroll 0 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1)
      .el-menu 
        background-color rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1)
        .el-menu-item 
          height 40px
          line-height 40px
          cursor pointer
          &:hover 
            color $color-white
          &.is-active 
            color $color-white
            background none 0px 0px repeat scroll rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3)
          span 
            font-size $font-size-medium
            color $color-aside-text
          i:before 
            font-size $font-size-medium-x
